ke":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T18:20:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T21:28:07.000Z","msg":"你都幫唔到佢手，仲煩佢！？"},{"pid":"2af71d3e9cfea07fa3289d2f5cfd3189d8a3dfa2","tid":2292780,"uid":259706,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T21:36:00.000Z","msg":"心思思想移民 但呢個係佢自己問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n睇黎佢唔打算同你有將來咁囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26e93e0e3a5e2b07eb6fb9d52bfc569419889ea3","tid":2292780,"uid":311783,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T21:38:27.000Z","msg":"有無諗過你就係心事苦惱既源頭，<br />\n所以佢先唔想搵你"},{"pid":"6fa60b74730443479a93a16eefc64010350e8fc4","tid":2292780,"uid":23141,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T21:40:46.000Z","msg":"真<br />\n女仔就係想人聽自己呻，唔需要建議<br />\n男仔反而就如果你幫唔到佢，佢就唔會講"},{"pid":"5210d6d893b245ab54a6c0589182e74f4c2bd752","tid":2292780,"uid":281775,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T21:44:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f75a26f9e07abf4c4a3964132f9478332bb848e3","tid":2292780,"uid":7212,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T23:58:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f398bcb4ba4006c563a3afdfe296338c9c2d131","tid":2292780,"uid":153223,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f75a26f9e07abf4c4a3964132f9478332bb848e3","tid":2292780,"uid":7212,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T23:58:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T01:36:08.000Z","msg":"屌好撚認同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8607d15e71ea11481351991df6c2c6f7075383db","tid":2292780,"uid":77393,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T04:45:37.000Z","msg":"係 想講自然會同你講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />女人真係好麻煩<br />\n<br />\nchur佢只有兩個下場<br />\n講咗 條女反而更加唔開心 要氹<br />\n唔講 條女繼續chur 嬲咗 又要氹<br />\n<br />\n建議樓主學下企喺對方角度諗 唔好將所有事同對方愛唔愛你掛勾就得<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13fbabb75dbcd2dea9aacb4fd0c72876cd6bac15","tid":2292780,"uid":171866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T17:10:33.000Z","msg":"講左你可能仲唔開心，又唔會幫到件事<br />\n<br />\n不如揾日服侍佢請佢食殘廢餐效果仲好"},{"pid":"7c4b6860186ccf3a70463cfe9fab108805804d11","tid":2292780,"uid":305718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T17:18:43.000Z","msg":"有時只不過想自己靜下啫 又或者真係有啲嘢唔同得你講呢 <br />\n我嘅話 太攰嘅時候真係好少主動搵人傾嘅 多數都係沉澱一下再呻 <br />\n畀啲空間佢啦 佢知道你喺度就得其實<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />祝福你哋喇"},{"pid":"f16efdc4875db76eb5b033cfb042d843336360ba","tid":2292780,"uid":329218,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T19:07:16.000Z","msg":"要睇你同佢關係點樣<br />\n我男朋友其實唔開心都中意自己一個<br />\n但係有時都會同我講佢煩惱嘅野<br />\n首先佢覺得你夠成熟可以幫你分擔<br />\n係一個好嘅聆聽者<br />\n而且佢係會將自己弱點表露出黎<br />\n唔係係年紀面前逞強果種<br />\n<br />\n就好似朋友咁<br />\n有d朋友係講唔太到心事，只係適合嘻嘻哈哈<br />\n你同佢係可以好似知己咁無所不談<br />\n佢就咩都會講（除非真係咩大件事到唔想你擔心/怕你嬲之類）"}]}